{"title":"Signature Mithai","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"motichur-laddu","title":"Motichoor Laddu","description":"\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"pro-des-title pro-info-box\"\u003e\n\u003ch2 data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eIndia's Favourite Laddu\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExperience the authentic taste of Dadu's Signature Motichoor Laddu, meticulously crafted with premium ingredients and time-honoured techniques. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eRenowned for its unmatched consistency in taste, texture, and form, this laddu is so soft it melts in your mouth with a gentle touch. It's no wonder that this sweet delight is one of the best sellers in India. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIndulge in the ultimate treat that embodies the rich tradition and exceptional quality Dadu's is known for.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMotichoor Laddu is a cherished delicacy with ancient roots in Hindu culture, especially popular during cultural \u0026amp; festive seasons, Dussehra, and Diwali, embodying the essence of Indian tradition.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003e\u003ca style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\" title=\"Watch how Dadu's Motichoor Laddu gets made\" href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/reel\/Chq9WTcBscZ\/?igsh=eTR1Yzk2ZDF6NmRo\"\u003eWATCH\u003c\/a\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e the craftsmanship in action\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eKey Features\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003ePremium Ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003eMade with the finest gram flour (besan), highest quality sugar, and pure desi ghee. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMinimalist Sugar Approach\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDadu's Motichoor Laddu provides a natural sweetness, with just the right amount of sugar and clarified butter added to achieve the perfect taste.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eArtful \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCraftsmanship\u003c\/strong\u003e\n\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePerfect \u003cem\u003edaana\u003c\/em\u003e and melt-in-your-mouth softness honed by decades of craftsmanship - a must try treat when travelling to Hyderabad\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https:\/\/dadus.co.in\/blogs\/premium-sweets-and-online-mithai-store\/indias-favourite-laddu\" title=\"Learn more about Dadu's Motichur Laddu\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eDiscover\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e why many across India consider Dadu’s Motichoor Laddu to be the best.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOrder Today\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eShop your favorite sweets online and enjoy our reliable delivery service. For a free tasting and a true gourmet experience, visit Dadu’s near you.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor international shipping inquiries, contact our support. Our clients within Hyderabad, India can get instant delivery using \u003ca title=\"Shop Dadu's Sweets Collection on Swiggy and get instant delivery\" href=\"https:\/\/www.swiggy.com\/menu\/2085?source=sharing\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eSwiggy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/a\u003